      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_Choices.Array.data[1]'
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_Choices.Array.data[2]'
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: _CurrentLines.Array.size
      value: 6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: I sigh as I gently close my journal and look up to see my surroundings.
        The living room feels homey, its walls decorated with portraits, with woodcraft
        for ventanilla and capiz windows from the 1860s.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: "Well, that's what it used to be\u2026 Now it's just muddied, destroyed,
        and worn down."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: "Hearing the news about Malabon\u2019s precious heritage zone being
        severely flooded the moment I woke up really put me on edge. Seeing what
        was left made my heart sink."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: "I decided to become a historian so I can study the conservation of
        international history, but the Raymundo house\u2026 I left it as is despite
        my parents saying it had belonged to one of our distant relatives."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: "And right now I\u2019m standing inside the living room, seeing it destroyed
        alongside the other remaining heritage houses. I couldn't help but feel like
        I had failed my mission as the house\u2019s caretaker and historian, even
        though the flooding wasn\u2019t my fault."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: "There\u2019s no use moping what\u2019s done is done. I might as well
        find anything left that is worth salvaging in this mess."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: "I couldn't help but feel like I had failed my mission as the house\u2019s
        caretaker and historian, even though the flooding wasn\u2019t my fault."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: "There\u2019s no use moping what\u2019s done is done. I might as well
        find anything left that is worth salvaging in this mess."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 686456765658737974, guid: ce2ab44ccbc9b3c4e96319afc399e6a7, type: 3}
      propertyPath: '_CurrentLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: "There\u2019s no use moping what\u2019s done is done. I might as well
        find anything left that is worth salvaging in this mess."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
